ist ul,\n      .activity-goods,\n      .activity-goods-box .price{\n          display: block;\n      }\n  <\/style>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"TagWrap\">\n\n\n\n<div id=\"PageBtm\">\n    <section class=\"faq-category-box\">\n        <ul uk-accordion=\"multiple: true\" class=\"faq-category-content\">\n            <li>\n                <a class=\"uk-accordion-title\" href=\"#\">Wigs for Men Near You<\/a>\n                <div class=\"uk-accordion-content\">\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">When it comes to this subject, there are two methods of keeping it stay on the head and they are using glues\/tapes or using clips.<\/span><\/p>\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">LaVivid delivers to most of the countries all over the world. LaVivid also works with a lot of salons in many countries\/places that people can get a professional wig installation and haircut locally, so you can get the best wig for men near you with LaVivid.<\/span><\/p>\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Here at LaVivid, our customer service team are more than happy to assist you pick out a suitable hair system for you. We are available through emails (<a href=\"mailto:support@lavividhair.com\">support@lavividhair.com<\/a>), phone calls (Monday-Friday, 9:00AM – 5:30PM PST,  TEL: 833-879-0279), and on Social media channels (Search LaVivid hair on <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/lavivid_hairreplacementsystem\/\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/LaVividhairsystem\/\" target=\"_blank\">facebook<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCWVHoRQV3rRfVe-5TqSpjog?view_as=subscriber\">youtube<\/a>). <\/span><\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/li>\n            <li>\n                <a class=\"uk-accordion-title\" href=\"#\">How does a wig stay on men?<\/a>\n                <div class=\"uk-accordion-content\">\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">When it comes to this subject, there are two methods of keeping it stay on the head and they are using glues\/tapes or using clips.<\/span><\/p>\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">If you start with a clip-on system, the standard procedure is to attach the system by positioning it on your head, opening each comb clip, gathering some growing hair inside, and snapping the clip closed.<\/span><\/p>\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">The most common method of attachment is to use hair tape or liquid adhesive to bond lace, skin, or mono wigs on your scalp.<\/span><\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/li>\n            <li>\n                <a class=\"uk-accordion-title\" href=\"#\">Will wigs fall off?<\/a>\n                <div class=\"uk-accordion-content\">\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">The answer to this question is that if the wig fits your head perfectly, the hair won't fall off. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">When we make the wig, there is a very important factory that we put on first priority which is the head curvature. <\/span><\/p>\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">If the curvature of the wig matches with your head, then it stays on your head quite firmly. With the help of bonding products, it will never fall off.<\/span><\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/li>\n            <li>\n                <a class=\"uk-accordion-title\" href=\"#\">Can wigs look good on men?<\/a>\n                <div class=\"uk-accordion-content\">\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Why not? Wigs are to make a man perfect in appearance. <\/span><\/p>\n                    <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">If the wigs are properly placed on the head and accurately fixed, they will certainly look good on men.<\/span><\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n    <\/section>\n\n    <div class=\"top-sellers-comment\">\n        <div class=\"trustpilot-logo\"><div><img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/create-a-wholesale-account\/topsellers20220124\/logo_trustpilot.gif\" alt=\"Trustpilot\"><\/div><\/div>\n        <ul>\n            <li><div class=\"sub-box\">\n                <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-pic\">\n                    <div>\n                        <strong style=\"background-color: #c1edd3;\">DB<\/strong>\n                        <span>Dan Becker<\/span>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n                <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-content\">\n                    <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-date\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/create-a-wholesale-account\/topsellers20220124\/ico_stars.png\" alt=\"stars\" class=\"ico_stars\">\n                        <span>Jan 19, 2022<\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <strong class=\"top-sellers-comment-content-sttl\">I FEEL LIKE A YOUNG MAN AGAIN<\/strong>\n                    <p>I have been bald since I was a teenager. I have always worn a hat every day for decades. The old days of men and their oh so obvious toupees never even tempted me until I found LAVIVID HAIR SYSTEMS for men! Lavivid changed my life! I have been a customer for 9 months now and love the EROS\/thin skin system. It looks so totally real that even family members who know that I am bald could not tell that it was not my real hair! Thank you so much for the HAIR SYSTEM!<\/p>\n<\/div>\n            <\/div><\/li>\n            <li><div class=\"sub-box\">\n                <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-pic\"><div>\n                    <strong style=\"backgro