T! I can style my hair however I want (even if I love my right parted quiff and I stick with that), the hairline is so undetectable and is a peace of mind. It's easy to maintain so it suits my lifestyle and it rarely tangles.<br>I can certainly say that I'll be a LaVivid Hair customer from now on and I'll never change it.<br>Thank you!<\/p>\n<\/div>\n            <\/div><\/li>\n\n            <li><div class=\"sub-box\">\n                <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-pic\"><div>\n                    <strong style=\"background-color: #c9e1ff;\">J<\/strong>\n                    <span>Ángel J Martínez<\/span>\n<\/div><\/div>\n                <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-content\">\n                    <div class=\"top-sellers-comment-date\">\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/create-a-wholesale-account\/topsellers20220124\/ico_stars.png\" data-src=\"https:\/\/d23tttlodvxe00.cloudfront.net\/img\/cms\/tag\/create-a-wholesale-account\/topsellers20220124\/ico_stars.png\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"108\" height=\"20\" alt=\"stars\" class=\"ico_stars\">\n                        <span>April 13, 2021<\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <strong class=\"top-sellers-comment-content-sttl\">LAVIVID REVIEW<\/strong>\n                    <p>I have been with LaVivid Hair since 2019 and I’ve always had GREAT wigs. Each one was always better than the other. I get thick skin base, and it’s absolutely wonderful to upkeep. I’ve been so grateful to have LaVivid hair, it’s easy to care for with the right products and conditioners. Smooth hair, voluminous, and lasts me longer than any other wig I’ve owned. This hair makes me feel confident and I’ve inspired other me. To give toupees a chance. Thank you LaVivid from the bottom of my heart ❤<\/p>\n<\/div>\n            <\/div><\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<script>\/* <![CDATA[ *\/;var cookieUsId=2625;$(function(){$(\".signOut\").click(func